 10:     Original cpptraj doc:
 11:     ====================
 12:         The abstract base class that all other actions inherit. 
 13:         By convention actions have 3 main phases: init, Setup, and DoAnalysis.
 14:         Init is used to initialize the action, make sure that all arguments
 15:         for the action are correct, and add any DataSets/DataFiles which will
 16:         be used by the action. Setup will set up the action for a specific
 17:         Topology file. DoAnalysis will perform the action on a given frame.
 18:         A fourth function, Print, is for any additional calculations or output 
 19:         the action may require once all frames are processed.
